  10 Nov 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>
  sylpheed-claws-0.9.4-r1.ebuild, sylpheed-claws-0.9.4.ebuild,
  sylpheed-claws-0.9.6-r1.ebuild:
  Fix ghostviewer plugin compile process to compile against the unpacked sources
  rather than an already installed instance of sylpheed-claws -- which will
  break if compiling -claws for the first time. Closes bug #32503 by Steve
  Arnold <nerdboy@gentoo.org>

